Name: TwoPlay Mahjong(双人麻将)
About the game: This is a Mahjong game from china.It is not four people game that is traditional chinese Mahjong game ,but it is two people game . This game has two mode:local game mode and network game mode.in local game mode,player will get coins by a virtual competitor and player's level up. in network game mode,player will play Mahjong game with another player from internet. If you wanna learn play Mahjong ,And this game will make you become an expert .
